name: Desjardins Emerging Markets Equity Index ETF
longDescription: The investment strategy of the ETF is to invest, directly or indirectly, in a portfolio of emerging markets that closely matches the Index. The index is composed of large and mid-cap securities of Emerging Markets companies. The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of an Emerging Market Equity Index. Currently, DMEE seeks to replicate the performance of the Solactive GBS Emerging Markets Large  Mid Cap CAD Index (CA NTR) (the index).
